casebody.data:
Vickie Yates Brown GLISSON, Secretary, Kentucky Cabinet for Health and Family Services, petitioner,
v.
D.O., et al. No. 17-17. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 10, 2017.

Motion of respondents for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
